    <p>{`Once you've installed Kerberos Enterprise, you will have the Kerberos Enterprise Factory webapp running inside your cluster. This web application allows you to administrate your Kerberos Enterprise agents as deployments/pods. It comes a bunch of other features as well, read on.`}</p>
